# Example .netrc file for PyAnsys UV Project
# Copy this content to ~/.netrc and configure your credentials
# IMPORTANT: Set permissions with: chmod 600 ~/.netrc

# =============================================================================
# PRIVATE REPOSITORY AUTHENTICATION
# =============================================================================

# GitHub with Personal Access Token
machine github.com
login your-username
password ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# GitLab with Personal Access Token  
machine gitlab.company.com
login your-username
password glpat-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Private PyPI Repository
machine your-private-pypi.com
login your-username
password your-api-token

# Artifactory or Nexus Repository
machine artifacts.company.com
login your-username
password your-password

# =============================================================================
# USAGE NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 
# 1. The .netrc file should be placed in your home directory: ~/.netrc
# 2. Set strict permissions: chmod 600 ~/.netrc
# 3. Use personal access tokens instead of passwords when possible
# 4. For GitHub, the username can be arbitrary when using tokens
# 5. Some services require specific token formats (like GitLab's glpat- prefix)
#
# =============================================================================